Package: loscolores
Title: Engineering-Grade Perceptual Color Systems
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Raimundo", "Sanchez", email = "raimundosanchezu@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A perceptual color system builder based on OKLab. Ensures luminance hierarchy, applies entropy safety to achromatic inputs, and provides robust manifolds for categorical, sequential, and divergent data visualization.
